title: Teyana Taylor Thanks Ariana Grande for Gift After Golden Globe Nods: ‘Honored to Share This Space’
summary: "I just wanted to say you are so brilliant," the Wicked star told her.
body: Ariana Grande couldn’t be happier for Teyana Taylor ‘s best supporting actress nomination at the 2026 Golden Globes — and vice versa.
